    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through an M-Variable locking differential. The mechanical integrity is superlative; the high-pressure VANOS system is silent, and critical preventative maintenance\u2014including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators\u2014has been meticulously documented. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing nuanced feedback across all drive modes. Finished in concours-level paint with zero swirl marks, the interior features Novillo leather with no bolster wear or compression. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
